<i>adverb</i>: 헛되이 [헏뙤이/헏뛔이], 한갓되이 [한갇뙤이/한갇뛔이], 괜히 [괜ː히], 괜스레 [괜ː스레], 공연히 [공연히], 공연스레 [공연스레] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>헛되이 [헏뙤이/헏뛔이]</dt><br>
<dd>vainly; fruitlessly</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 보람이나 실속이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of bearing no fruit or having no substance.</dd><br>
<dt>한갓되이 [한갇뙤이/한갇뛔이]</dt><br>
<dd>1. triflingly; insignificantly</dd><br>
<dd>중요하거나 특별할 것이 없어 겨우 하찮은 것밖에 안 되게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of considering something merely trivial without anything important or special.</dd><br>
<dd>2. vainly; fruitlessly</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 보람이나 실속이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of bearing no fruit or having no substance.</dd><br>
<dt>괜히 [괜ː히]</dt><br>
<dd>vainly; in vain; to no avail</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 이유나 실속이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without substance or particular reason.</dd><br>
<dt>괜스레 [괜ː스레]</dt><br>
<dd>vainly; in vain; to no avail</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 이유나 실속이 없는 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without substance or particular reason.</dd><br>
<dt>공연히 [공연히]</dt><br>
<dd>vainly; in vain; to no avail</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 이유나 실속이 없게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without substance or particular reason.</dd><br>
<dt>공연스레 [공연스레]</dt><br>
<dd>vainly; in vain; to no avail</dd><br>
<dd>특별한 이유나 실속이 없는 데가 있게.</dd><br>
<dd>Without substance or particular reason.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>